    <div data-cid="1112834">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1112834">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yuanrong/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u1390325-2.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yuanrong/" class="name">渡口</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2007-01-18" class="main-meta">2007-01-18 12:17:40</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1046265/">上海译文出版社2001版</a>
            </span>
    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1112834/">十年之痒</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1112834_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1112834">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        一直想写一篇关于《挪威的森林》的心得，10年了，也该动笔了。  我大概是中国第一代读村上春树书的人。   91年，一本书在南京的大学校园里悄悄流行，那是《挪威的森林》，不是林少华的版本，也不是赖明珠。我也赶时髦，在南京大学门口的书摊上买了一本，然后这本书10年没有搁下...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1112834-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1112834_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1112834_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1112834" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1112834">
                                9746
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="1112834" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-1112834">
                                321
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1112834/#comments" class="reply ">1073回应</a>

                    <a href="javascript:;;" class="fold hidden">收起</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

            
    
    <div data-cid="1496403">
